  "identifier": "SB 40",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to public library district boards of trustees.",
  "abstract": "Amend KRS 173.490 and 173.730 to allow a county judge/executive to fill vacancies on a library board, with the approval of the fiscal court, without being required to consider recommendations made the board or the state librarian if the county has adopted an alternative appointment process.",
